OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe heatwave continues on
OL,6,FSaturday with another dry and sunny
OL,7,Fday. Feeling hot with high UV but a
OL,8,Fmore notable breeze developing
OL,9,Fthroughout the day. Strong gusts
OL,10,Faround the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining dry and warm across
OL,13,Fthe region this evening perhaps with a
OL,14,Ffew patches of low cloud in the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FAnother very hot, dry and
OL,17,Fsunny day for most with strong
OL,18,Fsunshine and brisk winds. A chance of
OL,19,Fa few afternoon showers. Windy around
OL,20,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
