OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FRemaining largely dry, hot and sunny
OL,7,Fin the outlook. However, cloud will
OL,8,Fincrease a little on Monday and
OL,9,FTuesday with the chance of a few
OL,10,Fshowers and the odd thunderstorm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
